{"id":8558,"date":"2025-09-22T10:50:18","date_gmt":"2025-09-22T10:50:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/realtrips.in\/?post_type=trip&#038;p=8558"},"modified":"2025-12-04T11:47:28","modified_gmt":"2025-12-04T11:47:28","slug":"ahmedabad-dwarka-somnath-vadodara-kevadiya","status":"publish","type":"trip","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/trip\/ahmedabad-dwarka-somnath-vadodara-kevadiya\/","title":{"rendered":"AHMEDABAD DWARKA SOMNATH VADODARA KEVADIYA"},"content":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":8837,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","destination":[103],"activities":[],"trip_types":[75],"difficulty":[],"trip_tag":[],"wptravelengine_custom_taxonomy_tripcategory":[77],"class_list":["post-8558","trip","type-trip","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","destination-explore-gujarat","trip_types-customized-domestic-tour","tripcategory-customized-domestic-tour"],"packages_ids":[8562],"trip_extras":[],"cut_off_time":{"enabled":false,"duration":0,"duration_unit":"days"},"booked-seats":[],"code":"WTE-8558","price":27777,"has_sale":false,"sale_price":0,"discount_percent":0,"currency":{"code":"INR","symbol":"&#8377;"},"duration":{"days":6,"nights":5,"duration_unit":"days","duration_type":"days"},"min_pax":1,"max_pax":"","discount_value":0,"discount_label":"&#8377;0 Off","primary_category":27,"available_times":{"type":"default","items":["2021-1-01","2021-2-01","2021-3-01","2021-4-01","2021-5-01","2021-6-01","2021-7-01","2021-8-01","2021-9-01","2021-10-01","2021-11-01","2021-12-01"]},"description":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Journey through Gujarat\u2019s spiritual, cultural, and modern icons in one enriching trip. Begin in <strong>Ahmedabad<\/strong>, a UNESCO World Heritage City, where Sabarmati Ashram, Adalaj Stepwell, and bustling bazaars showcase history and tradition. Continue to <strong>Dwarka<\/strong>, one of the sacred Char Dham pilgrimage sites, where the Dwarkadhish Temple stands majestically on the Gomti riverbank. Head to <strong>Somnath<\/strong>, home to the legendary Somnath Temple, one of the twelve Jyotirlingas, offering deep spiritual and cultural significance. Explore <strong>Vadodara<\/strong>, known for the grand Laxmi Vilas Palace, museums, and vibrant art scene. Conclude at <strong>Kevadiya<\/strong>, home to the world\u2019s tallest statue\u2014the <strong>Statue of Unity<\/strong>, honoring Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel, surrounded by beautifully developed gardens, laser shows, and eco-tourism attractions. This tour perfectly blends <strong>heritage, spirituality, and modern marvels<\/strong>, making Gujarat an unforgettable destination.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->","cost_includes":" 3 star premium hotel stay\n All transfers and sightseeing by AC Vehicle\n Breakfast, Dinner, Lunch\n Toll Tax\n Parking\n Driver Allowance\nTravel Goodies\n 24 x 7 On tour Assistance\n All cost from EX Destination","cost_excludes":" Any meals other than those mentioned above in inclusions\n Airfare \/ Train Ticket\n GST 5%\n All monument entry Fees\n Any portage at airports and hotels, tips, insurance, wine, mineral water, telephone charges, and all items of personal nature\n Any services not specifically mentioned in the inclusions\nEntrance fees to Monuments & other sightseeing points\nExpenses caused by factors beyond our control like rail and flight delays, roadblocks, vehicle malfunctions, political disturbances, etc.\nAnything not mentioned in inclusions","itineraries":[],"faqs":[{"title":"1. What is the ideal duration for this trip?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A 6 to 7-day itinerary is recommended to cover Ahmedabad, Dwarka, Somnath, Vadodara, and Kevadiya comfortably.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"2. What are the highlights of Ahmedabad? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sabarmati Ashram, Adalaj Stepwell, Sidi Saiyyed Mosque, Kankaria Lake, and heritage walks in the old city.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"3. Why is Dwarka significant?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dwarka is one of the Char Dham pilgrimage sites and is famous for the Dwarkadhish Temple dedicated to Lord Krishna.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"4. What makes Somnath special? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Somnath Temple is one of the twelve Jyotirlingas of Lord Shiva and holds immense historical and religious importance.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"}],"is_featured":false,"featured_image":{"width":374,"height":226,"file":"2025\/09\/ahmdabad-dwarka-somnath-vedodara-kevadiya.png","filesize":153672,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"ahmdabad-dwarka-somnath-vedodara-kevadiya-300x181.png","width":300,"height":181,"filesize":68559,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ahmdabad-dwarka-somnath-vedodara-kevadiya-300x181.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"ahmdabad-dwarka-somnath-vedodara-kevadiya-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":33150,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ahmdabad-dwarka-somnath-vedodara-kevadiya-150x150.png"},"blog-sidebar-size":{"file":"ahmdabad-dwarka-somnath-vedodara-kevadiya-100x100.png","width":100,"height":100,"filesize":8182,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ahmdabad-dwarka-somnath-vedodara-kevadiya-100x100.png"},"blog-sidebar-size-thumb":{"file":"ahmdabad-dwarka-somnath-vedodara-kevadiya-90x80.png","width":90,"height":80,"filesize":6181,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ahmdabad-dwarka-somnath-vedodara-kevadiya-90x80.png"},"blog-post-two":{"file":"ahmdabad-dwarka-somnath-vedodara-kevadiya-342x226.png","width":342,"height":226,"filesize":101754,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/